snippet.title: Fast Multiplication of any number - using vedic math
snippet.description:
This maths trick for fast multiplication allows you multiply any two numbers quickly, using vedic math. This method is a great alternative either for those who need that extra bit of help with math, or people who like to expand their knowledge.
This trick is especially useful in multiplying large numbers, with less mess and confusion than standard long multiplication. To support free math by tecmath onPatreon (thankyou): https://www.patreon.com/tecmath To donate to the tecmath channel:  https://paypal.me/tecmath?locale.x=en_AU
